1
00:00:01,170 --> 00:00:03,740
(Episode 96)

2
00:00:08,080 --> 00:00:09,080
Father.

3
00:00:09,880 --> 00:00:12,080
Please let me explain everything.

4
00:00:12,150 --> 00:00:14,250
I wonder what lies
she's going to tell now.

5
00:00:14,350 --> 00:00:16,150
Lying is what she does best.

6
00:00:16,250 --> 00:00:19,120
Seo Rin, you of all people
don't need to be like this.

7
00:00:19,120 --> 00:00:20,990
The nerve.

8
00:00:21,060 --> 00:00:22,960
Father, I'll explain everything.

9
00:00:23,430 --> 00:00:26,100
Please, just hear me out first.

10
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:27,670
What more is there to hear?

11
00:00:28,430 --> 00:00:31,540
You dared to deceive me for 30 years?

12
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:35,540
And you still have the audacity
to say more?

13
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:39,310
No, Father.
This is all a misunderstanding.

14
00:00:39,580 --> 00:00:41,150
I never deceived you, Father.

15
00:00:41,150 --> 00:00:43,210
More lies!

16
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:46,680
How dare you try to deceive me
to the very end?

17
00:00:46,950 --> 00:00:50,020
How long will you keep lying
through your teeth?

18
00:00:50,420 --> 00:00:52,860
Did you think your secret
would last forever?

19
00:00:54,230 --> 00:00:55,730
How despicable.

20
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:59,000
- Father, it's not like that.
- That's enough, CEO Chae.

21
00:00:59,330 --> 00:01:02,270
Your pathetic excuses won't work anymore.

22
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:06,070
You're better off coming clean
and begging Grandfather for forgiveness.

23
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:07,270
Shut up, Oh Jang Mi.

24
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:10,580
What did I ever do
to deserve this from you?

25
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,940
I should be the one asking that.

26
00:01:13,580 --> 00:01:16,080
Seo Rin, you know
how much I love you, right?

27
00:01:16,510 --> 00:01:18,550
You know full well how I raised you.

28
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:21,450
You're my daughter.
My own flesh and blood.

29
00:01:21,620 --> 00:01:22,720
Stop it.

30
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:26,290
We did a DNA test.
Grandfather knows you're not my mother.

31
00:01:28,090 --> 00:01:31,930
Seo Rin. You're mistaken.
You are my daughter.

32
00:01:31,930 --> 00:01:32,930
Enough!

33
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:36,940
Stop making a fool of me
and get out of my house this instant!

34
00:01:37,170 --> 00:01:38,870
- Father.
- With the twins standing...

35
00:01:38,940 --> 00:01:42,640
right in front of me,
what more needs to be said?

36
00:01:43,270 --> 00:01:46,680
That's enough.
I don't need to hear another word.

37
00:01:46,980 --> 00:01:48,350
You're despicable.

38
00:01:50,750 --> 00:01:54,190
Please forgive me, Father. I was pregnant.

39
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:58,660
You knew I was pregnant
with Dong Seok's child, Father.

40
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:03,500
But that tramp, Jung Suk Hee,
pushed me down the stairs,

41
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,100
and my baby died!

42
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:10,100
That wench Jung Suk Hee
killed your own flesh and blood!

43
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,870
Please believe me.

44
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:15,870
- Jung Suk Hee is your enemy, Father.
- Stop lying, Chae Hwa Young!

45
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:18,680
How dare you blame my mother
for your miscarriage?

46
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:23,310
You stole Seo Rin from my innocent mother,

47
00:02:23,380 --> 00:02:25,350
and she had to jump into a river
just to save me.

48
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,950
And she's been suffering ever since.

49
00:02:27,950 --> 00:02:29,690
And because of you, Chae Hwa Young,

50
00:02:29,690 --> 00:02:32,190
people point fingers at her
and call her an idiot.

51
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:36,530
I'll never forgive you
for what you did to our mother,

52
00:02:36,690 --> 00:02:38,030
for what you did to me and Seo Rin,

53
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,730
and for murdering our father
to cover it all up.

54
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,570
- I will never forgive you!
- Shut up!

55
00:02:43,940 --> 00:02:46,540
- What do you know?
- That is enough!

56
00:02:47,410 --> 00:02:48,740
Get out of my house right now!

57
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,640
Father, please.

58
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:56,450
No matter what anyone says,
Seo Rin is my daughter.

59
00:02:57,150 --> 00:03:00,120
I lovingly raised her for 30 years.

60
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:04,020
You know that, Father.
You know how much I cherished her.

61
00:03:04,020 --> 00:03:05,420
I don't want to hear it.

62
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:09,560
Even my patience has its limits.

63
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:12,000
I've had enough, so get out now.

64
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:14,270
Never set foot in this house again!

65
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:17,070
And step down immediately as CEO!

66
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,770
Resign as CEO?

67
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:23,710
No.

68
00:03:24,940 --> 00:03:26,140
I won't do that.

69
00:03:27,050 --> 00:03:31,650
I poured everything into Dream Hotel.
Why should I step down?

70
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:34,090
You wretched woman.

71
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:37,390
And you still have more to say?

72
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:42,790
I've known your true colors for a while,
but your shamelessness knows no bounds.

73
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:49,330
From now on, don't you dare come near
Dream Hotel or the twins.

74
00:03:49,730 --> 00:03:52,740
If I ever see your face again, I'll...

75
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:56,110
Grandfather!

76
00:03:56,110 --> 00:03:58,710
Yes, die. Just die, you old bastard!

77
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:02,510
You think you can take everything from me?
Not a chance.

78
00:04:02,650 --> 00:04:04,220
Die. Just die!

79
00:04:05,220 --> 00:04:06,750
Grandfather...

80
00:04:09,490 --> 00:04:10,490
Father!

81
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:13,290
Pack your things.

82
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:21,300
She's finally getting kicked out.

83
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:23,100
Quiet. She'll hear you.

84
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:26,700
So what if she does?
Chae Hwa Young's reign is over.

85
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,880
Grandfather.

86
00:04:34,180 --> 00:04:37,550
I'm okay. Don't you worry.

87
00:04:37,850 --> 00:04:38,850
Grandfather.

88
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:42,020
You can't get sick
now that I'm here, okay?

89
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,090
Of course, sweetheart.

90
00:04:51,230 --> 00:04:52,230
Grandfather.

91
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,100
Yes, Jang Mi.

92
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:59,500
I should have known you were my family.

93
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:00,910
I'm so sorry.

94
00:05:01,610 --> 00:05:05,280
You and your mom have gone through
so much, haven't you?

95
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:06,980
Grandfather.

96
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:11,880
I will make the injustice
you've suffered right.

97
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,860
That old bastard.

98
00:05:19,490 --> 00:05:21,430
Does he think I'll go down this easily?

99
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:23,260
Not a chance.

100
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:25,560
He completely underestimated me.

101
00:05:26,230 --> 00:05:28,900
My husband told you to get out.
Why are you still standing there?

102
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:31,500
Have you no shame?

103
00:05:32,170 --> 00:05:33,170
What was that?

104
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:35,710
- The nerve!
- CEO Chae.

105
00:05:35,970 --> 00:05:38,780
Actually, since you're about
to be fired as CEO,

106
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:40,580
you're not really the CEO anymore,
are you?

107
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:42,550
Ms. Chae Hwa Young.

108
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:45,250
The way you've mistreated my mom
all this time,

109
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,850
I've been biting my tongue.

110
00:05:48,220 --> 00:05:50,860
Look at this pair, ganging up on me.

111
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:53,890
What are you going to do about it now?

112
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:55,790
You think this is the end for me?

113
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:58,230
If you don't leave,
do you think this is your house?

114
00:05:58,730 --> 00:06:00,970
My husband told you to get out,
so you'd better leave.

115
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,300
He wants you out immediately.

116
00:06:05,300 --> 00:06:07,370
We'll pack up your things,

117
00:06:07,810 --> 00:06:08,870
so you can pick them up later.

118
00:06:08,940 --> 00:06:10,540
See? What did I say?

119
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:13,610
Don't you dare touch me!

120
00:06:14,010 --> 00:06:16,450
Who do you think you are to kick me out?

121
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:19,220
I'm leaving on my own.
Now get out of my way.

122
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,230
Seo Rin.

123
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:34,500
I'm sorry.

124
00:06:56,220 --> 00:06:57,220
Mom.

125
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,400
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

126
00:07:10,130 --> 00:07:11,640
He's kicking me out just like that?

127
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:15,110
Who made Dream Hotel what it is today?

128
00:07:15,670 --> 00:07:16,940
No matter what anyone says,

129
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:18,810
I'm the one who built it.
Me, Chae Hwa Young.

130
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:21,410
Only I deserve Dream Hotel.

131
00:07:21,410 --> 00:07:23,350
Who are they to throw me out?

132
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,750
Don't worry, ma'am.

133
00:07:25,450 --> 00:07:27,650
They can't just get rid of you
that easily.

134
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:30,520
Besides, all the board members
are on your side.

135
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:34,930
That's right.
Get Director Park on the phone now.

136
00:07:35,730 --> 00:07:36,930
Do you understand, Director Park?

137
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,360
Good.

138
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:43,430
If word of this gets out,
our stock price will take a major hit.

139
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:45,900
So...

140
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,470
make sure you handle this discreetly.

141
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,610
What? Twins?

142
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,510
My goodness.

143
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:58,150
I'm sorry I didn't tell you sooner, Mom,

144
00:07:58,950 --> 00:08:02,050
but the woman Jun Ho brought home
as Seo Rin...

145
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,750
is actually Oh Jang Mi, the woman I love.

146
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,320
What?

147
00:08:07,020 --> 00:08:10,560
So that young woman isn't Director Ma,
she's Oh Jang Mi?

148
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,700
- Yes.
- What on earth?

149
00:08:15,230 --> 00:08:16,570
Now it all makes sense.

150
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:21,010
So that's why you were so against
your brother's marriage.

151
00:08:22,610 --> 00:08:23,610
My poor boy.

152
00:08:24,140 --> 00:08:26,140
You must have been going through
so much heartache.

153
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:29,650
It's okay. Don't worry, Mom.
Everything will work out now.

154
00:08:30,450 --> 00:08:31,450
Okay.

155
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:33,920
But how can CEO Chae...

156
00:08:34,450 --> 00:08:36,990
be so wicked?

157
00:08:38,460 --> 00:08:39,620
The nerve of her to think...

158
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:41,460
she could raise a child
that wasn't even hers for 30 years...

159
00:08:41,830 --> 00:08:44,000
and completely fool the Chairman.

160
00:08:44,530 --> 00:08:46,130
She kidnapped an infant,

161
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:49,800
so legally, that's kidnapping and fraud.

162
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:52,670
She could get serious jail time for that.

163
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,940
We'll have to wait and see
what the Chairman decides to do.

164
00:08:58,010 --> 00:09:00,210
What's all this about?

165
00:09:00,710 --> 00:09:02,880
CEO Chae stole one of the twins?
Is that really true?

166
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:06,050
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

167
00:09:09,050 --> 00:09:10,120
Mom.

168
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:22,930
Ok Hee, Tok Hee.

169
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:25,670
My baby.

170
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:37,210
It's Ok Hee, Tok Hee.
Ok Hee and Tok Hee are here.

171
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:40,690
Ok Hee and Tok Hee are so cute.

172
00:09:44,290 --> 00:09:46,520
(Yoogane Spicy Chicken)

173
00:09:46,660 --> 00:09:47,760
Here it comes.

174
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:50,160
Here's the spicy stir-fried chicken
you ordered.

175
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:53,460
- Enjoy.
- Thank you.

176
00:09:53,730 --> 00:09:54,730
Looks great.

177
00:09:54,730 --> 00:09:58,740
This dinner is to celebrate you two,
so dig in.

178
00:09:59,100 --> 00:10:00,100
Okay.

179
00:10:01,170 --> 00:10:03,910
It looks too good to eat.

180
00:10:04,810 --> 00:10:08,180
This looks delicious.
Look at that cheese stretch!

181
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:11,850
You're right.
I've never had nachos with this.

182
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:13,150
I wonder how it'll taste.

183
00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:18,760
It's so crunchy and delicious.

184
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,730
Mom, here, let me make you a wrap.

185
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:26,060
With some cheese...

186
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,230
and flying fish roe.

187
00:10:28,230 --> 00:10:30,500
It should be amazing. Here, Mom, open up.

188
00:10:34,070 --> 00:10:35,070
It's good, right?

189
00:10:35,540 --> 00:10:36,540
It's delicious.

190
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:40,410
Stir-fried chicken is definitely best
on a hot plate like this.

191
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:46,320
And for the perfect finish,
these cold buckwheat noodles are a must.

192
00:10:46,620 --> 00:10:50,090
The broth is so tangy and refreshing,
you just can't stop eating it.

193
00:10:50,290 --> 00:10:53,390
- Go on, try some.
- Mom, let me make you one too.

194
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:55,860
Here.

195
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:01,070
It's delicious.

196
00:11:21,690 --> 00:11:22,690
Is it finally...

197
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:24,360
all out in the open now?

198
00:11:25,490 --> 00:11:26,490
Yes.

199
00:11:28,030 --> 00:11:29,060
Don't you worry, Jun Ho.

200
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:30,900
I'm not going down like this.

201
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:33,700
Do you know what I've been through
to get here?

202
00:11:34,370 --> 00:11:36,470
You think a little thing like this
will make me crumble?

203
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,000
Not a chance.

204
00:11:41,170 --> 00:11:42,170
My dear son.

205
00:11:44,110 --> 00:11:45,940
You're just worried about me, aren't you?

206
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:03,090
I've wanted to ask you this
for a long time.

207
00:12:05,430 --> 00:12:06,600
Who is my father?

208
00:12:08,770 --> 00:12:10,270
I never asked before...

209
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,770
because it felt like I was accepting you
as my mother.

210
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:20,910
Who is my father?

211
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:23,180
Jun Ho...

212
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:38,960
Are you...

213
00:12:39,900 --> 00:12:41,570
finally accepting me as your mother?

214
00:12:45,570 --> 00:12:46,570
Thank you.

215
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:48,640
Thank you.

216
00:12:59,980 --> 00:13:00,990
Who is...

217
00:13:02,020 --> 00:13:03,090
Jun Ho's father?

218
00:13:05,090 --> 00:13:07,320
- What?
- I'm asking about Jun Ho's father.

219
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:09,860
Who is Jun Ho's biological father?

220
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:11,660
Why are you asking me that?

221
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:15,430
He has nothing to do with you.
Jun Ho is my son, and mine alone.

222
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:19,270
Then I'll do some digging
and find out myself...

223
00:13:21,610 --> 00:13:23,040
who Jun Ho's real father is.

224
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:36,050
Year 1990...

225
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:38,690
May 29.

226
00:13:44,860 --> 00:13:47,430
(August 1989)

227
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,640
Coming all the way to the film set...

228
00:14:00,180 --> 00:14:01,280
in this downpour...

229
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:05,020
Look at the state I'm in.

230
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:09,090
I barely landed this supporting role,

231
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,820
and you're just now telling me
that I've been replaced?

232
00:14:14,190 --> 00:14:16,230
I'm sorry. I just found out myself.

233
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:19,600
I think Mr. Kim cast
one of his other starlets.

234
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:22,570
She's nowhere near as good as you, though.

235
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:23,970
Forget it.

236
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:28,140
You think that's supposed
to make me feel better?

237
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:32,740
I'm cold.

238
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:36,450
You can't catch a cold.

239
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:06,840
Hwa Young.

240
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:11,050
Don't you see me as a woman?

241
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,620
I'm cold.

242
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,890
So warm me up with your body.

243
00:15:34,570 --> 00:15:35,570
Chae Hwa Young.

244
00:15:36,340 --> 00:15:37,910
No matter how much you deny it,

245
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,640
Kang Jun Ho is my son.

246
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,990
Shouldn't you be heading home?

247
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:56,660
I just needed to clear my head.

248
00:15:57,390 --> 00:15:59,260
Is there something you want to tell me?

249
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:03,530
Go on.

250
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:06,000
Whatever it is, it's okay.
You can tell me.

251
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,910
I'm sorry.

252
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:12,710
I've been hiding something from you.

253
00:16:13,710 --> 00:16:14,750
What is it?

254
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:17,750
General Manager Kang Jun Ho's
biological mother...

255
00:16:19,920 --> 00:16:21,150
is Chae Hwa Young.

256
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:24,320
What did you just say?

257
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:26,290
I found out by accident,

258
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:29,890
and I couldn't believe it,
so I had a DNA test done,

259
00:16:30,930 --> 00:16:31,960
and it was a match.

260
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:34,300
That's impossible.

261
00:16:36,100 --> 00:16:37,100
Then...

262
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,000
Does...

263
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:41,000
Jun Ho know about this?

264
00:16:45,710 --> 00:16:46,710
It must have...

265
00:16:47,310 --> 00:16:48,750
been so hard for him.

266
00:16:48,950 --> 00:16:52,220
I'm sorry I didn't tell you sooner,
Baek Ho.

267
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:55,150
I was worried about how shocked you'd be,

268
00:16:55,490 --> 00:16:56,720
so I couldn't bring myself
to say anything.

269
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:01,160
Jang Mi,

270
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:03,860
don't try to carry this all on your own.

271
00:17:04,760 --> 00:17:05,760
And...

272
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:09,070
from now on,
let's be honest with each other like this.

273
00:17:09,530 --> 00:17:10,600
No more secrets.

274
00:17:11,840 --> 00:17:13,800
You don't hate me?

275
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:15,570
Yes, I do.

276
00:17:17,570 --> 00:17:18,780
But just as much,

277
00:17:19,940 --> 00:17:21,010
I love you even more.

278
00:17:21,350 --> 00:17:22,410
Thank you.

279
00:17:23,410 --> 00:17:26,720
And I will be your strength from now on.

280
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:30,050
Stay strong, Baek Ho.

281
00:17:36,390 --> 00:17:39,060
Grandfather,
I'm going back to work, starting today.

282
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:43,000
Seo Rin, focus on your health.

283
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,230
I'm perfectly healthy.

284
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:46,600
I'm going to take my rightful place
at the company.

285
00:17:46,670 --> 00:17:49,010
If you come back,
the staff will be confused.

286
00:17:49,840 --> 00:17:51,070
They won't know what to make
of Oh Jang Mi.

287
00:17:52,010 --> 00:17:53,010
Jin Hong Ju.

288
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:55,210
Do you have a problem with me going back
to the company?

289
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:56,780
It's not that...

290
00:17:57,210 --> 00:17:59,650
Let's be honest,
you're only doing this to see Jun Ho.

291
00:18:00,350 --> 00:18:02,690
Since when have you ever cared about work?

292
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:07,120
- Oh Jang Mi is better at this job.
- What did you just say?

293
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:09,060
I'm the original.

294
00:18:09,330 --> 00:18:12,230
When the real deal shows up,
the fake has to get out of the way.

295
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:16,300
Seo Rin,
let's just focus on your health for now.

296
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:19,200
You need surgery on your face first.

297
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:25,310
Good morning, Grandfather.

298
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:26,480
Hi, Seo Rin.

299
00:18:27,710 --> 00:18:29,150
Welcome, Jang Mi.

300
00:18:29,610 --> 00:18:31,550
We have plenty of rooms here.

301
00:18:31,980 --> 00:18:33,750
Why did you go back to the side dish shop?

302
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:36,520
My mom is still not feeling well.

303
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:39,090
Besides,
I need to give Seo Rin her place back.

304
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:42,360
Good. While you're at it,
give my man Jun Ho back too.

305
00:18:50,370 --> 00:18:52,470
Minister, please hear me out.

306
00:18:52,470 --> 00:18:53,470
Minister!

307
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,770
Why would you hang up
before even hearing me out?

308
00:18:58,380 --> 00:18:59,480
Am I a joke to him?

309
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:01,510
Unbelievable.

310
00:19:02,950 --> 00:19:05,950
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

311
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:07,050
This can't be happening.

312
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:09,790
How could every single one of them
turn their backs on me?

313
00:19:10,520 --> 00:19:12,690
Especially after taking all my money.

314
00:19:13,690 --> 00:19:15,230
This can't be.

315
00:19:18,230 --> 00:19:19,330
CEO Chae Hwa Young.

316
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:24,400
You stole another person's child
and passed her off as a wealthy heiress.

317
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:26,240
You kept up that lie for 30 years.

318
00:19:26,570 --> 00:19:29,010
Legally,
that constitutes abduction of a minor,

319
00:19:29,410 --> 00:19:30,610
as well as enticement.

320
00:19:30,870 --> 00:19:33,840
Not to mention ordering evidence disposal
to cover your tracks.

321
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:36,810
Do you have any idea how long
the indictment against you is?

322
00:19:37,110 --> 00:19:38,950
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

323
00:19:39,980 --> 00:19:41,520
You could always turn yourself in.

324
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:43,820
- How about it?
- Shut your mouth, Oh Jang Mi.

325
00:19:44,350 --> 00:19:45,790
This is all your fault.

326
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:50,260
Voluntarily resign as CEO of Dream Hotel,
effective today.

327
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:53,800
If you insist on making this ugly,
we'll add abuse of power to the charges...

328
00:19:54,060 --> 00:19:55,730
and request an arrest warrant for you.

329
00:19:56,170 --> 00:19:58,440
Lawyer Kang Baek Ho will make sure of it.

330
00:20:00,540 --> 00:20:02,510
Give me a break. That'll never happen.

331
00:20:02,570 --> 00:20:03,970
You dare to come after me?

332
00:20:04,040 --> 00:20:07,840
I just hope that your downfall
doesn't bring down Dream Hotel with you.

333
00:20:09,610 --> 00:20:11,180
Escort her out.

334
00:20:14,180 --> 00:20:17,150
Let go of me. Get your hands off of me!

335
00:20:17,650 --> 00:20:19,360
Do you know who I am? Move!

336
00:20:20,290 --> 00:20:24,090
If you so much as lay a finger on me,
I'll kill every last one of you!

337
00:20:24,330 --> 00:20:26,600
Will being dragged out kicking
and screaming make you feel better?

338
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:31,070
What did you say?
You really have no fear, do you?

339
00:20:32,140 --> 00:20:34,100
Let me go! I said, let go!

340
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,270
I built this company!

341
00:20:37,270 --> 00:20:38,980
You're all fired!

342
00:20:39,210 --> 00:20:41,680
I'm the CEO of this company! How dare you!

343
00:20:41,810 --> 00:20:44,310
You think it's over for me just like that?
Not a chance!

344
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,880
Let go!

345
00:20:49,090 --> 00:20:50,720
This hasn't even been approved
by the board yet.

346
00:20:51,150 --> 00:20:52,560
Why are you removing the CEO Chae?

347
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:54,160
The board's approval is imminent.

348
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:57,060
We'll say your resignation is
for health reasons.

349
00:20:57,690 --> 00:20:58,760
Leave with some dignity.

350
00:20:59,760 --> 00:21:00,760
Unbelievable...

351
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,600
I'll be back. Just you wait.

352
00:21:17,180 --> 00:21:19,120
You've been through a lot, Jang Mi.

353
00:21:19,380 --> 00:21:20,820
It's not over yet.

354
00:21:21,180 --> 00:21:23,550
We still haven't brought Chae Hwa Young
to justice.

355
00:21:23,690 --> 00:21:25,920
Then you need to be the one
to show Chae Hwa Young...

356
00:21:26,220 --> 00:21:27,390
that you can't get away
with defying the law...

357
00:21:27,690 --> 00:21:30,490
and stealing another person's life.

358
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:33,430
Baek Ho.

359
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:36,870
Thank you for trusting me
and waiting for me.

360
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:40,740
I always had faith in you, Jang Mi.

361
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:43,110
I knew you would come back to me.

362
00:21:49,310 --> 00:21:52,250
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

363
00:22:11,230 --> 00:22:12,240
Jun Ho.

364
00:22:13,070 --> 00:22:14,240
Don't hang your head.

365
00:22:14,970 --> 00:22:16,670
That doesn't suit you.

366
00:22:17,710 --> 00:22:19,310
I'm sorry you have to see me like this.

367
00:22:20,040 --> 00:22:21,080
My son.

368
00:22:22,310 --> 00:22:24,820
You boasted that you would give me
Dream Hotel.

369
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:28,120
What happened
to the confident CEO Chae Hwa Young?

370
00:22:28,690 --> 00:22:29,690
Where is she?

371
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:33,660
Pull yourself together.

372
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:35,430
I'll help you.

373
00:22:39,230 --> 00:22:40,230
Stay strong.

374
00:22:41,670 --> 00:22:42,670
Mom.

375
00:23:05,360 --> 00:23:08,530
You're right.
I can't just give up like this.

376
00:23:09,090 --> 00:23:12,360
No matter what, the Dream Hotel is mine.
It's my Jun Ho's.

377
00:23:13,330 --> 00:23:17,530
There has to be a way.
No, there has to be.

378
00:23:54,700 --> 00:23:56,670
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

379
00:24:07,650 --> 00:24:08,650
Don't think...

380
00:24:09,390 --> 00:24:10,920
this is the end.

381
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:16,290
Because I'll do whatever it takes
to make you mine.

382
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:20,530
You just don't know when to quit,
do you, General Manager Kang?

383
00:24:22,300 --> 00:24:24,030
Don't make me get cruel.

384
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:27,340
- General Manager Kang.
- Pushing me away makes me more resolved.

385
00:24:28,410 --> 00:24:30,310
I'll take you away from him,
no matter what it takes.

386
00:24:30,610 --> 00:24:32,440
Do you think Baek Ho stole me from you?

387
00:24:33,080 --> 00:24:34,910
Is that why,
like a child with a stolen toy,

388
00:24:34,910 --> 00:24:37,650
you're throwing a tantrum to get me back?

389
00:24:38,980 --> 00:24:40,580
Had my toy taken away?

390
00:24:41,790 --> 00:24:44,050
Were you ever even mine to begin with?

391
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:47,620
This is a longing for something
I've never had.

392
00:24:48,190 --> 00:24:49,960
That's how much I love you.

393
00:24:50,030 --> 00:24:51,190
That isn't love.

394
00:24:51,860 --> 00:24:53,300
It's obsession and stubborn pride.

395
00:24:53,500 --> 00:24:55,830
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

396
00:24:56,430 --> 00:24:58,670
Call it obsession or stubbornness.
I don't care.

397
00:24:59,970 --> 00:25:02,110
I'll do whatever it takes to have you.

398
00:25:02,110 --> 00:25:03,140
Stop it.

399
00:25:03,570 --> 00:25:05,280
I was the one who chose Baek Ho.

400
00:25:05,780 --> 00:25:09,550
He didn't choose me. I chose him.

401
00:25:09,950 --> 00:25:12,280
So, Jun Ho, you never lost anything,

402
00:25:12,850 --> 00:25:14,780
which means you have no reason
to be angry.

403
00:25:15,690 --> 00:25:16,690
No.

404
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:19,120
I'm taking this all the way.

405
00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:23,560
Just remember that the only person
who can stop me is you, Jang Mi.

406
00:25:24,360 --> 00:25:25,700
I won't stop.

407
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:30,330
Because you're the only one
holding the brakes.

408
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:38,640
Seo Rin.

409
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:45,920
Jun Ho.

410
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:51,390
Do you really love Oh Jang Mi and not me?
Is that it?

411
00:25:51,450 --> 00:25:53,760
No, Seo Rin. It's not like that. I just...

412
00:25:53,820 --> 00:25:56,190
Oh Jang Mi, stay out of this.
I'm asking Jun Ho.

413
00:25:59,260 --> 00:26:01,630
Jun Ho, answer me.

414
00:26:02,430 --> 00:26:05,270
Do you really love Oh Jang Mi?

415
00:26:05,900 --> 00:26:06,900
Yes.

416
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:09,210
I love her more than
anything in this world.

417
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:13,610
And I am going to marry her,
no matter what.

418
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:19,520
Seo Rin!

419
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,120
Seo Rin!

420
00:26:22,250 --> 00:26:23,290
Seo Rin!

421
00:26:36,430 --> 00:26:38,170
My love.

422
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:43,370
After losing you and Eun Hye like that,

423
00:26:44,710 --> 00:26:46,880
I don't know
how I can still be breathing...

424
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:49,580
or how I can go on living like this.

425
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:54,750
There's just so much going on.

426
00:26:58,590 --> 00:26:59,590
Honey.

427
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:04,030
Am I being punished?

428
00:27:05,260 --> 00:27:07,630
But at least I found
our Dong Seok's daughters,

429
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:10,870
the twins.

430
00:27:19,540 --> 00:27:23,380
Grandma, are you making a
four-leaf clover bracelet?

431
00:27:23,510 --> 00:27:24,680
Yes.

432
00:27:25,020 --> 00:27:26,250
You're so pretty, Bo Ra.

433
00:27:26,650 --> 00:27:28,890
I'm making this for you, Bo Ra.

434
00:27:28,950 --> 00:27:30,690
Yes! I'm so excited!

435
00:28:10,790 --> 00:28:12,330
(The First Man)

436
00:28:12,430 --> 00:28:14,130
This is driving me crazy, too.

437
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:15,200
Okay, fine.

438
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:18,740
But in return, you have to keep
Jun Ho being my mom's son a secret.

439
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:21,040
She's not even fighting back.

440
00:28:21,370 --> 00:28:22,810
Assault, Article One.

441
00:28:22,810 --> 00:28:26,010
Committing an assault is subject
to a fine of up to 5,000 dollars.

442
00:28:26,310 --> 00:28:28,340
- Mom...
- You have to do me a favor, too.

443
00:28:28,510 --> 00:28:31,250
You said you had evidence
in the Oh Bok Gil murder case, right?

444
00:28:31,410 --> 00:28:32,620
There's a wrench.

445
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,650
A wrench? Where is it?

446
00:28:38,190 --> 00:28:40,190
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
